	* bin/devdiscover.in: New option: --limit=regexp

2004-03-17  Stanislav Sinyagin  <ssinyagin@users.sourceforge.net>

	* NEWS: Release 0.1.5

	* lib/Torrus/DB.pm (new): Unique DB environment log file per PID. 

