	* xmlconfig/snmp-defs.xml, xmlconfig/*/*.xml: data-file refers now
	to system-id, instead of snmp-host.

	* lib/Torrus/DevDiscover.pm (buildConfig): symbolic-name is no longer
	mandatory. New parameter: system-id.

